description:
###### 50% OFF #####
* In our life time is most valuable. Most of time we are wasting most of the valuable time on facebook.
* You might think to quit this habit. By using this app you can quit the habit of facebook.
* This application can be very effective in monitoring and tracking time on facebook.
* This application is effective because keeping track of how you are spending time on facebook is an important because to save most valuable time on facebook.
* You can enter multiple facebook logs per day.
* Search your logs based on the note.

Features:

* Efficient & effective way of tracking your facebook timings.
* You can enter multiple logs per day.
* Attractive user interface & quick navigations possible.
